    <description>Approval Process for &quot;Revenue Request&quot; record type for Account Request object.v3.  Adding in a step to route to Cash at the end.  This process is entered if MAX Adjustment Amt GREATER OR EQUAL $5001 and less than 100K.
v6 Added Submitted to Finance Manager status.
Breakout for North
Created  for AE Approving manager Master DOS
1-10-21 Updated for new Division and Regions Process 23 - Renaming to East from North
Local V4 Updated for 2023 Sales Re Org
V5 Updates for Finance and Fulfillment (SRSF-4588)</description>
    <emailTemplate>Account_Request/Acct_Request_Approval_Process_Notification</emailTemplate>
    <enableMobileDeviceAccess>false</enableMobileDeviceAccess>
    <entryCriteria>
        <booleanFilter>1 AND 2 AND 3 AND 4 AND 5 AND 6</booleanFilter>
        <criteriaItems>
            <field>Account_Request__c.RecordType</field>
            <operation>equals</operation>
            <value>Revenue Adjustment</value>
        </criteriaItems>
        <criteriaItems>
            <field>Account_Request__c.Status__c</field>
            <operation>equals</operation>
            <value>New,Denied,Recalled</value>
        </criteriaItems>
        <criteriaItems>
            <field>Account_Request__c.MAX_Adjustment_Amt__c</field>
            <operation>greaterOrEqual</operation>
